item.title: Mary Poppins Act I at the Ethel Merman Theatre Sydney
item.description:
Mary Poppins Act I at the Ethel Merman Theatre Sydney

This is a full scale working model of the London/Broadway production of Mary Poppins. The set includes 128 channels of programmable LED lights, 6 stepper motors to control the truck lines & a LED data projector for the projections.
